      {
        "Language": "ENG",
        "Name": "The Blue Bomber\u0027s Best Bud",
        "Client": "Senri the Mailman",
        "Description": "I\u0027ve got a special quest fur-om\r\nthe Mega Man series for ya!\r\nThere\u0027s a Zinogre in there that\r\nmay be small, but I have a bone\r\nto pick with. Hunt it, and I\u0027ll\r\ngive you the materials to forge\r\nMega Man\u0027s trusty companion!",
